1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,780
=Episode 4=

3
00:01:07,239 --> 00:01:08,799
Starting today,

4
00:01:08,799 --> 00:01:10,920
you are my personal attendant.

5
00:01:11,519 --> 00:01:14,200
You'll handle all my daily needs.

6
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:18,280
I came to be a needle,

7
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:18,719
not...

8
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:20,239
If you can't even handle this,

9
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:22,120
how can you be a good needle?

10
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:23,719
My Lord,

11
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,359
the hot water is ready.

12
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,359
Noted.

13
00:01:28,719 --> 00:01:29,760
Your first task

14
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,519
is to help me bathe.

15
00:01:33,799 --> 00:01:35,159
(What?)

16
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,680
Help me undress.

17
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:58,599
(He helped me today.)

18
00:01:58,959 --> 00:02:00,400
(Could it be...)

19
00:02:18,319 --> 00:02:19,919
(Now she's)

20
00:02:19,919 --> 00:02:21,400
(acting shy?)

21
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,280
(Oh no.)

22
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,639
(Is he really going to...)

23
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:03,759
Enough.

24
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,400
What are you waiting for?

25
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:21,280
Come serve me.

26
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:24,719
(So this is)

27
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:26,560
(his test?)

28
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,719
You said you wanted

29
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:49,240
to be my needle.

30
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,879
But that's not what you meant, is it?

31
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,680
Mutual benefit

32
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,639
is the key to longevity.

33
00:04:05,199 --> 00:04:07,240
I doubt that's all.

34
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:11,759
The moment you touched Rong Xiu

35
00:04:11,759 --> 00:04:13,439
that day,

36
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:15,919
you knew your elder sister's death

37
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:17,879
was connected to Consort Rong.

38
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,199
So you plotted to kill her.

39
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,879
Using yourself as bait

40
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,439
to avenge your sister.

41
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:32,040
It seems everyone who harmed her,

42
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:34,120
you intend to make them all pay.

43
00:04:39,319 --> 00:04:40,759
What about me,

44
00:04:40,759 --> 00:04:42,319
who sent her body back?

45
00:04:46,319 --> 00:04:47,360
Your Majesty!

46
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,360
Your Majesty!

47
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,480
Do you know

48
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,920
the forces in this palace

49
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,439
cannot be overthrown

50
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:54,519
by Divine Power alone?

51
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:59,079
A mere Holy Maiden keeping
your Zhao land alive,

52
00:04:59,079 --> 00:05:00,920
that's already a good deal.

53
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:04,000
If you insist on your own way,

54
00:05:04,759 --> 00:05:06,639
your entire tribe

55
00:05:07,199 --> 00:05:08,279
will perish.

56
00:05:08,460 --> 00:05:12,460
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

57
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,360
Excuse me.

58
00:05:16,780 --> 00:05:20,340
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

59
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:22,660
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

60
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:26,860
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

61
00:05:27,300 --> 00:05:28,940
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

62
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:30,460
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

63
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:33,660
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

64
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:36,240
Can't take a few words of advice?

65
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,380
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

66
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,439
Then how will you avenge your sister?

67
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:44,100
♪I can't forget the stars in your eyes♪

68
00:05:44,100 --> 00:05:47,660
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

69
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,879
You misunderstand, My Lord.

70
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:54,319
I was only trying to serve you.

71
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,279
My Lord, do you care about your wounds?

72
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,399
My Lord!

73
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:04,839
My Lord!

74
00:06:09,399 --> 00:06:10,680
What happened?

75
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,639
Perhaps

76
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,360
you should see for yourself.

77
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:21,040
That young man

78
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,319
you took from His Majesty

79
00:06:23,199 --> 00:06:24,079
is...

80
00:06:24,639 --> 00:06:26,759
Dying is the easiest thing in the world.

81
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:28,319
Hurry, get him down.

82
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:28,720
Go.

83
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,319
Yes.

84
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,160
In the palace,

85
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:38,360
do not misuse your Divine Power.

86
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,959
If you get caught,

87
00:06:39,959 --> 00:06:41,879
the entire plan will fall apart.

88
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,800
In three days,

89
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,800
you will perform before the court.

90
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:48,959
Rong Xiu and Rong Zhaohua
will both be there.

91
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,319
Train hard.

92
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,759
Do not slack off.

93
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,560
That mute young man

94
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,040
you took from His Majesty

95
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,360
couldn't take the torment.

96
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,160
Last night,

97
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,399
he hanged himself.

98
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:10,279
(A man taken from the Emperor?)

99
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:15,279
He was so handsome.

100
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:17,439
Lord Nine-Thousand must be devastated.

101
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:25,920
I dare to ask for this servant

102
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:29,920
Let me send him to the Nanfeng Pavilion

103
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,639
and train him myself.

104
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:35,639
I haven't even had my fun yet.

105
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,639
How dare he die so easily?

106
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,800
Send his body to my chamber.

107
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,000
Yes.

108
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:43,279
Yes.

109
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,800
(It seems)

110
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:49,000
(I've found your weakness.)

111
00:07:56,839 --> 00:07:57,519
My Lord,

112
00:07:57,519 --> 00:07:59,319
I made this tea especially for you.

113
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,120
You must be tired.

114
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,399
Let me help you change.

115
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:39,559
My Lord,

116
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,080
are you pleased?

117
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:06,679
My Lord,

118
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,600
what are you doing?

119
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:09,919
Naturally,

120
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:12,039
I'm trying to please you.

121
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:17,679
What those men wouldn't do for you,

122
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:20,600
I can make them do.

123
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,519
None of them can compare to you.

124
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:36,440
If you like it,

125
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,799
it's my honor.

126
00:09:54,799 --> 00:09:57,080
(You're clearly not into women.)

127
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,919
(How long can you keep up the act?)

128
00:09:58,919 --> 00:10:00,279
You're testing me?

129
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,320
Fine.

130
00:10:02,799 --> 00:10:03,240
Strip.

131
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,840
Let's see if you bare it all.

132
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,799
You eunuch!

133
00:10:09,799 --> 00:10:11,080
Come out!

134
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,600
Even if I die here today,

135
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,960
I will see you!

136
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,399
Come out!

137
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,240
Move!

138
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,080
You must leave today!

139
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:20,000
I've told you many times, madam,

140
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:20,639
your son's death

141
00:10:20,639 --> 00:10:22,360
had nothing to do with us.

142
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:24,240
How can it be unrelated?

143
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,720
You must go!

144
00:10:26,159 --> 00:10:26,840
My Lord.

145
00:10:33,759 --> 00:10:35,720
Give me back my son!

146
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:38,480
You are a monster!

147
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,240
You should be thanking me.

148
00:10:48,639 --> 00:10:50,879
Your son had an affair
with Noble Lady Lin.

149
00:10:50,879 --> 00:10:52,480
Given the Emperor's temper,

150
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:55,120
he would have been torn apart.

151
00:10:57,399 --> 00:11:00,080
My son became a eunuch

152
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,960
to serve Lady Lin.

153
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,519
How could he get her pregnant?

154
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:07,039
Dying before the Emperor

155
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:09,399
is better than being taken
by a eunuch like you

156
00:11:09,399 --> 00:11:11,200
and tormented

157
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:13,960
until he lost his dignity.

158
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:16,120
I'm in a good mood today.

159
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:18,000
I won't stoop to your level.

160
00:11:18,759 --> 00:11:19,840
Get her out.

161
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:20,679
What are you waiting for?

162
00:11:20,679 --> 00:11:21,600
Take her away.

163
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,879
Don't let her bother My Lord.

164
00:11:23,279 --> 00:11:23,759
Move.

165
00:11:23,759 --> 00:11:26,279
You'll pay for this someday.

166
00:11:26,279 --> 00:11:29,200
I'll haunt you even as a ghost!

167
00:11:29,799 --> 00:11:30,720
Tomorrow at noon,

168
00:11:31,039 --> 00:11:32,559
prepare a carriage out of the city.

169
00:11:35,039 --> 00:11:36,879
The Emperor cut you open

170
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:38,639
just to check the baby's gender.

171
00:11:38,639 --> 00:11:39,720
How absurd.

172
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:42,799
Have you named the child?

173
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,360
Not yet.

174
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,759
Please give him a name.

175
00:11:45,759 --> 00:11:48,039
May he never suffer in life.

176
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:49,759
Let's call him Fu.

177
00:11:52,159 --> 00:11:52,840
Fu,

178
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,159
you have a name now.

179
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,399
My Lord,

180
00:11:55,399 --> 00:11:55,799
I...

181
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:57,399
I never imagined

182
00:11:57,399 --> 00:11:59,440
you would do so much for this.

183
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,080
I don't know how to...

184
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:00,919
It was nothing.

185
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,519
Say no more.

186
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,320
It's dangerous here.

187
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,279
Get on the road now.

188
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:08,039
Thank you for saving us.

189
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,440
I can't take this.

190
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:18,320
I can't accept any more kindness.

191
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,679
The child needs food.

192
00:12:19,919 --> 00:12:20,600
You need this.

193
00:12:24,919 --> 00:12:25,919
(Someone's here.)

194
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:28,600
Go.

195
00:12:46,039 --> 00:12:47,360
(Trying to run?)

196
00:12:58,399 --> 00:12:59,159
(Oh no!)

197
00:13:18,460 --> 00:13:19,860
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

198
00:13:20,340 --> 00:13:21,780
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

199
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:25,100
♪No one knocks upon the mountain gate♪

200
00:13:25,420 --> 00:13:29,220
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

201
00:13:32,180 --> 00:13:33,900
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

202
00:13:33,900 --> 00:13:35,420
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

203
00:13:35,780 --> 00:13:39,180
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

204
00:13:39,180 --> 00:13:43,180
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

205
00:13:44,340 --> 00:13:47,500
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

206
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:51,060
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

207
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:53,380
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

208
00:13:53,380 --> 00:13:57,580
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

209
00:13:58,020 --> 00:13:59,660
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

210
00:13:59,660 --> 00:14:01,180
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

211
00:14:01,180 --> 00:14:04,380
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

212
00:14:04,780 --> 00:14:06,700
♪In dreams, it's you♪

213
00:14:06,700 --> 00:14:08,100
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

214
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:11,420
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

215
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:14,820
♪I can't forget the stars in your eyes♪

216
00:14:14,820 --> 00:14:18,380
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

217
00:14:18,380 --> 00:14:21,620
♪In this mortal world, there is only us♪

218
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:25,060
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
